@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="about-section">
    <p>Welcome to our Recipe Sharing Application!</p>

    <p>Our platform is dedicated to bringing food enthusiasts together from all around the world. Whether you're an aspiring home cook or an experienced chef, we offer a space where you can:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Share your unique recipes</strong>: Upload and showcase your favorite dishes, complete with ingredients, step-by-step instructions, and photos.</li>
        <li><strong>Discover new recipes</strong>: Browse through a variety of recipes shared by users worldwide, ranging from quick meals to gourmet dishes.</li>
        <li><strong>Connect with fellow food lovers</strong>: Comment on recipes, exchange tips, and be part of a vibrant community that loves to cook and share culinary experiences.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Our mission is to inspire creativity in the kitchen and make recipe discovery and sharing easier and more fun. From baking the perfect cake to exploring international cuisine, there's something for everyone!</p>

    <h2>Features of Our Application</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Recipe Search:</strong> Quickly find any recipe by entering keywords or ingredients.</li>
        <li><strong>Recipe Upload:</strong> Easily upload your own recipes, complete with images and detailed instructions.</li>
        <li><strong>User Profiles:</strong> Keep track of your favorite recipes, see what others are cooking, and share your culinary journey.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>We believe that cooking brings people together, and through our platform, we aim to foster a community that thrives on creativity, inclusivity, and a shared passion for good food. Our recipe-sharing app is designed to be user-friendly, making it easy for anyone, from novice cooks to seasoned chefs, to share their love of food.</p>

    <p>Thank you for being a part of our community and happy cooking!</p>
</div>

<!-- Optional: Style for the about section -->
<style>
    .about-section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .about-section h2 {
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .about-section ul {
        list-style-type: square;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .about-section li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
</style>
